   RULES AND PROCEDURES

   COMPILATIONS
     * Circuit Rules of the United States Court of Appeals for the
       District of Columbia Circuit, effective January 3, 2000 - together
       with the corresponding Federal Rules of Appellate Procedure, as
       amended December 1, 1998

     * Handbook of Practice and Internal Procedures effective January 3,
       2000

     * Rules of the Judicial Council  for the District of Columbia Circuit
       Governing Complaints of Misconduct or Disability as amended August
       10, 2001.

     * Complaint Form


     Criminal Justice Act (CJA) Plan (Effective July 1, 1991; and amended
   April 8, 1996, October 23, 1996, and March 19, 1998)
     * May 26, 1998 - Notice of amendment to the Court's Plan to Implement
       the Criminal Justice Act of 1964 ("CJA") and guidelines to assist
       counsel in meeting this specificity requirement.
     * February 19, 1998 - Notice regarding Public Disclosure of CJA
       Payments
     * Letter to Court Appointed Counsel

     * Model Letter Withdrawing at Certiorari Stage


     Frequently Asked Questions, and Answers, Concerning Court and Clerk's
   Office Operations (August 2001)

